{"tid":2333852,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"燈神媽咪麵開Po睇好3隻重磅科技股　網民喊驚：聖誕節都想股災？","createTime":"2020-12-20T17:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T12:42:40.000Z","uid":66271,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c095cc38d1718508865c0d730803ed480bb9d0dd","tid":2333852,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T17:59:35.000Z","msg":"【麵咪媽／連登討論區／燈神】著名連登燈神媽咪麵早前驚揭確診末期腦癌，於是發起眾籌希望網民可以支持醫療費，最後籌得逾68萬元，加上1間慈善組織給予等同30萬元的資助後，他已正式開始療程。<br />\n<br />\n媽咪麵在治療期間亦不忘給予一眾連登仔及股民「明燈指示」，他近日就開Po表示看好ATMXJ中的其中3隻股票，建議買入。網民見狀立即叫苦連天，該3隻股票都是恒指成份股，大嘆媽咪麵「聖誕節都想股災」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200601/344149554091921409.jpeg/WU2Gg-TgkQpiE8ZWqS7Qa4WgbKbgD9mVGuMjdhrjI3Y?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200601%2F344149554091921409.jpeg%2FWU2Gg-TgkQpiE8ZWqS7Qa4WgbKbgD9mVGuMjdhrjI3Y%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=b1b17cb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n媽咪麵在帖文表示，自己強烈推介3隻股票，「益埋你哋班正股投資者」，當中包括受螞蟻暫延上市困擾的阿里巴巴（9988）、股王騰訊控股（700）及美團點評（3690）。媽咪麵推介的3隻股票皆為恒生指數成份股，行業亦屬科技股。<br />\n<br />\n媽咪麵表示，看好阿里是因為股價未有跌穿250天平均線，「唔好問幾錢入好，瞇埋眼入就得」。騰訊表現更優於阿里，因為連100天線也未曾跌穿，「都係唔好問幾錢入好，瞇埋眼入就得」。最後他就指美團雖然似是跌穿10天、20天及50攻線，「但睇真啲你就會覺得係假穿，依家呢個位入，1個字，Sure Win呀」。媽咪麵最後表示，「呢3隻股王就當我媽咪哥送畀大家嘅聖誕禮物啦，Merry Christmas」。"},{"pid":"56cb7d074971c373600e6aa1820837340205029c","tid":2333852,"uid":373438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T20:18:27.000Z","msg":"XG01又抄文啦？"},{"pid":"70e6151f2ece70f8321d2d36508c87b9e3c3cda7","tid":2333852,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T22:40:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6656340faf1fe03efd748cebad802b0472738c8","tid":2333852,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:39:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc95a0f60a3737ed06359af6627bc36205464f1","tid":2333852,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d87102c9f3ab606a86d0ade6ecaaf2e56d0bbae","tid":2333852,"uid":169116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:31:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d32caa818bb0245dfdc2ba28c59fc298caaa920","tid":2333852,"uid":190310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:53:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ywC3tr8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FywC3tr8.gif&h=3e78cd2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44b1febd8adf0f29a7a4ee2f3a7488cdeee39079","tid":2333852,"uid":316420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T11:55:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />新聞行業咁易做"},{"pid":"0bb8b2a7f37fd67b95b79825e279081b310b85e5","tid":2333852,"uid":306495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"連登公海連登"},{"pid":"01e36cddff9342ff059767710838d0ea8f842649","tid":2333852,"uid":167597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:42:40.000Z","msg":"信面神，唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}